{"tid":623262,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"為部分港鐵線增設通勤快速","createTime":"2018-04-10T00:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T12:47:04.000Z","uid":108894,"like":6,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b14477c6644a9e2d00b7ba0ed3aa0e5996f736d4","tid":623262,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:21:39.000Z","msg":"香港幾十年都冇呢種路線，所有線全停真係慢左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而且港鐵頂閘嚴重 ，根本有時停站都上唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以其實真心可以考慮通勤快線，尤其東鐵同西鐵<br />\n<br />\n建議如下:<br />\n東鐵快速: 不停太和，大學，火炭<br />\n西鐵快速: 不停朗屏，錦上路，柯士甸<br />\n荃灣線快速: 不停大窩口，長沙灣<br />\n觀塘線快速: 不停樂富，石硤尾<br />\n馬鞍山線快速: 不停恆安，大水坑，沙田圍，車公廟<br />\n港島線快速: 不停西營盤，炮台山，西灣河<br />\n機場快線快速: 機場直通香港<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳線，東涌線，南港島線車站較少唔需要<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee00c766a2508b26c543c1945cccbf18894dbff8","tid":623262,"uid":33703,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:22:47.000Z","msg":"無空間俾你飛站 完"},{"pid":"64a5a936c3541607dfebf383266c9c198d4f2fb9","tid":623262,"uid":27303,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"ee00c766a2508b26c543c1945cccbf18894dbff8","tid":623262,"uid":33703,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:22:47.000Z","msg":"無空間俾你飛站 完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:23:29.000Z","msg":"認同 此post已完"},{"pid":"1f4c9723c683fb395e835d3feb68d756c417167a","tid":623262,"uid":84081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:23:34.000Z","msg":"荃灣線訊號問題加單軌做唔到"},{"pid":"9f69f4d368da8c122d663db84139990f4e5875c6","tid":623262,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:23:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e46bafd8dedd5b01bdfa7a20360dfb8553130d20","tid":623262,"uid":73123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:24:25.000Z","msg":"剩係單向單程狗鐵都搞到成pat屎咁啦仲點搞急行線<img src=\"/asset